    <div class="row justify-content-between align-items-center">
      <div class="col-lg-5 col-xl-4">
        <div class="mil-mb-90">
          <h2 class="mil-up mil-mb-60">Meet <br>Our Team</h2>
          <p class="mil-up mil-mb-30">We are engineers, architects, and problem solvers who thrive on building software that works. Every member of our team brings deep technical expertise and a shared commitment to quality.</p>
          <p class="mil-up mil-mb-60">From cloud infrastructure to frontend interfaces, our diverse skills combine to deliver robust, scalable solutions for every client.</p>
          <div class="mil-up"><a href="/team" class="mil-button mil-arrow-place mil-mb-60"><span>Read more</span></a></div>
          <h4 class="mil-up"><span class="mil-thin">We</span> build <br><span class="mil-thin">exceptional</span> software.</h4>
